{"tid":1295144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[update] 眾籌登報+公投+人權法庭","createTime":"2019-07-08T02:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T18:42:17.000Z","uid":275176,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e767f581c4c9d8a3e4ee50d160cbb3006d9f5495","tid":1295144,"uid":275176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"想澄清幾樣<br />\n<br />\n-P 牌信唔過&gt; 已經有搞聯署既絲打endorse <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258799\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258799</a><br />\n7月1號hk watch都有post個聯署出黎, 去英國既係BNOCC group<br />\n-Bno令事件失焦&gt; 今日咁既局面既根源係joint declaration, jd出事就有無限可能, 退一步我地爭取緊繼承權, 令bno子女都受保障<br />\n-唔中意連登&gt; 個別成員的確唔中意連登, 請見上個post畀人不斷屈做hkip, 而呢個係group acc, 所以言論有時有d 激; 但脫歐tory labour黨內成員都有唔同意見<br />\n-同Hkip既關係&gt; DOVC係主力搞公投，但冇人理<br />\n只好用眾籌想引起關注, 公投結果要由HKIP幫我地交上國會<br />\n-其他合作組織&gt; 我地係三個組織一齊發起<br />\nDOVC+HKIP+BNOCC group, 但個別人士不斷spin去hkip<br />\n-我地同攬炒巴打分別&gt; 兄弟爬山; 因為我地全部係英國組織, 所有訴求全部係對英國<br />\n1. BNO問題，叫英國唔好再避<br />\n2. 中英聯合聲明已經係歷史文件，咁英國係需要保障在香港英國國民人權<br />\n<br />\nBNO CC group畀五毛搞過，佢地已經上咗年紀，但佢地係最出心出力<br />\n問緊佢地可唔可以畀fb link <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1457138397739962/posts/2224412061012588/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1457138397739962%2Fposts%2F2224412061012588%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b05c71ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1457138397739962/posts/2224412061012588/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係bnocc同dovc一齊做嘅聯署<br />\nbnocc親自交上去<br />\n<br />\ndovc<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Descendants-of-Victoria-City-2267996923412983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDescendants-of-Victoria-City-2267996923412983%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=2b5d6af8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Descendants-of-Victoria-City-2267996923412983/</a><br />\n新嘅組織，為公投同bno而成立<br />\n我地仲需要人<br />\n唔介意可以幫下手<br />\n<br />\nhkip<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongIndependenceParty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongIndependenceParty%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=232f82cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongIndependenceParty/</a><br />\n大家可能唔多like hkip<br />\n但佢真係幫我地做咗好多<br />\n<br />\n我地已經睇咗價, 費用係ard 20 萬hkd 1個full page<br />\n已經send左email畀the guardian sales team<br />\n大家想用咩圖，請幫手諗<br />\n初步諗係屎忽or細路仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Dear Prime Minister, <br />\nWhen will you face your shameful retreat from Hong Kong?<br />\n<br />\n圖<br />\n<br />\nWe, the Hong Kong citizens, as the &quot;users&quot; under the Declaration, are telling you the Declaration has failed, the &quot;one country, two systems&quot; has failed.<br />\n<br />\nThe Chinese government has already announced the Sino-British Joint Declaration is null and void. Why are you hiding?<br />\n<br />\nWe teach kids how to face problems, not to hide.<br />\nSo please review the rights of British National (Overseas), and act on your obligation to protect your nationals in Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，真係想大家支持個公投<br />\n因為HKIP聯絡埋美國，如果真係多人想公投<br />\n我地就會盡快搞<br />\n我地相信公投係可以令全世界明白香港人究竟想點<br />\n<br />\n你地繼續屌我地唔緊要<br />\n屌完入fb投個票<br />\n香港人要有民主政府，首先要話畀全世界知你地係會相信民主<br />\n我唔係話要獨立，但連獨立都唔敢提，自己先滅自己聲，又點爭取民主？<br />\n民主係可以容納唔同聲音又互相尊重<br />\n我地要做到畀全世界知我地係值得擁有民主自由<br />\n<br />\n想捐錢嘅我地都多謝你地<br />\n捐唔捐都好<br />\n入fb投個票<br />\n想要定唔要個公投<br />\n由你地決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/declaration-for-the-breach-of-sino-british-joint-declaration/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fdeclaration-for-the-breach-of-sino-british-joint-declaration%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=cd8a6bd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/declaration-for-the-breach-of-sino-british-joint-declaration/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後講下歐洲人權公約<br />\nECHR俄佬同火雞2個都係締約國, 都畀人告過<br />\n同歐盟冇關<br />\n所以脫唔脫歐冇關係<br />\n<br />\n有咩問即管問<br />\n關於公投/眾籌都請隨便問"},{"pid":"49374806556daafd5f6a8a14dba1a887256386fd","tid":1295144,"uid":275176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee346de150d58a3484a6a8f1c08d695c4643019","tid":1295144,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0478332fd8787238630b234f6ecfa8f4b1fe88ba","tid":1295144,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d1e5b1af8276f961e7503e23dbda6864f7aa7f","tid":1295144,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b4406fb33ebba0bbd768f407479c99e678a47cf","tid":1295144,"uid":275176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26cf54f995bb0d09dcc1c49dd9fef8376dc5c24","tid":1295144,"uid":275176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7474ea3b1bd5c08afa391db0e8f67af2a0ad0b0f","tid":1295144,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b55110af2a9251a48fdb1ee23b7e4c29139b66","tid":1295144,"uid":107572,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n請問打官司嗰度詳情係點？"},{"pid":"8db68e816f626d89ce575f7c83d501d40ee8c973","tid":1295144,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"